RTS Stock-Index Futures Fall 0.3% at Start of Trading

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-04-25T15:07:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-25/rts-stock-index-futures-fall-0-3-at-start-of-trading.html
Russia ’s RTS futures expiring in
June fell 0.3 percent to 198,210 at 11:02 a.m. in  New York .  OAO Gazprom, the natural-gas export monopoly, declined 0.1
percent. Contracts on OAO Lukoil, the country’s second-biggest
oil producer, slid 0.1 percent, while contracts on OAO Sberbank,
Russia’s largest lender, lost 0.1 percent.  The Market Vectors Russia ETF, a U.S.-traded fund that
holds Russian shares, dropped 1.2 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
